 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1752/modkey-stops-working-after-entering-resize-mode/?answer=1754#post-id-1754</link><description>You must return to "default mode". I think by default this is done with Escape. Have a look into your config file, inside of the 'mode "resize"' section should be a command like &lt;code&gt;bindsym Escape mode "default"&lt;/code&gt;, but you can use any key you want there.</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2013 07:26:39 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1752/modkey-stops-working-after-entering-resize-mode/?answer=1754#post-id-1754</guid></item></channel></rss>